1번 문제 답안.

인덱스 변경.
create index IX_T_EMP23_B on T_EMP23 (DIV_CODE, DEPT_CODE)
tablespace USERS
pctfree 10
initrans 2
maxtrans 255
storage
(
  initial 64K
  next 1M
  minextents 1
  maxextents unlimited
);
  
< 변경 전>
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Id  | Operation                   | Name       | Starts | A-Rows |   A-Time   | Buffers |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|   0 | SELECT STATEMENT            |            |      1 |     93 |00:00:00.04 |    4393 |
|*  1 |  TABLE ACCESS BY INDEX ROWID| T_EMP23    |      1 |     93 |00:00:00.04 |    4393 |
|*  2 |   INDEX RANGE SCAN          | IX_T_EMP23 |      1 |   7271 |00:00:00.01 |      16 |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

< 변경 후>
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Id  | Operation                   | Name         | Starts | A-Rows |   A-Time   | Buffers |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|   0 | SELECT STATEMENT            |              |      1 |     93 |00:00:00.01 |      94 |
|   1 |  TABLE ACCESS BY INDEX ROWID| T_EMP23      |      1 |     93 |00:00:00.01 |      94 |
|*  2 |   INDEX RANGE SCAN          | IX_T_EMP23_B |      1 |     93 |00:00:00.01 |       2 |
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


2번 문제 답안.

인덱스 변경.
create index IX_T_CUST22_02 on T_CUST22 (FLAG, DIV, CUST_CD)
tablespace USERS
  pctfree 10
  initrans 2
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 64K
    next 1M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );

